text.english: By the word of the LORD the heavens were made, And all the host of them by the breath of His mouth. For He spoke, and it was done; He commanded, and it stood fast.
text.arabic: بِكَلِمَةِ الرَّبِّ صُنِعَتِ السَّمَاوَاتُ وَبِنَسَمَةِ فَمِهِ كُلُّ جُنُودِهَا. لأَنَّهُ قَالَ فَكَانَ. هُوَ أَمَرَ فَصَارَ.
